{"title":"fix(remediation): set REQUIRED_API_BASE to http://app-backend:80 to fix nginx proxy_pass syntax error","body":"Root cause: The nginx container fails because REQUIRED_API_BASE environment variable is set to empty string in the Deployment, causing the ConfigMap template to render invalid nginx config with "proxy_pass ;" syntax.

Evidence: nginx: [emerg] invalid number of arguments in "proxy_pass" directive in /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf:8

Affected resources: Deployment/vigil-app, Pod/vigil-app-547945c74-zv4x5","auto_merge":true}
